'''Body-wood''' was the finest luxury wood of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. It resembled the flesh of the natives of its planet before the [[Palpatine/Legends|Emperor]] claimed the world. Pale pink in color, it was shot through with scarlet streaks, which slowly bled out after the wood was harvested. Some believed body-wood trees sustained a certain intelligence and they were said to cry when cut down. The wood gave off a pink glow when harvested. [[Lord/Legends|Lord]] [[Hethrir]] of the [[Empire Reborn]], was granted exclusive right to harvest it by the [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]], and made his fortune selling it. Hethrir also used the wood extensively for his own use, paneling his private office on his [[worldcraft]] with it.

